## 6. Out-of-Scope for v1

- User authentication and saved favourites.
- Advanced filtering (date ranges, opponent, home/away).
- Statistical leaderboards and rankings.
- Head-to-head player comparisons.
- Export to CSV or clipboard.
- Embedded charts or visualisations.
- Push notifications or live score updates.

