## 8. Dependencies and Risks

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| balldontlie.io API downtime | Low | High | Surface clear error; add link to API status page |
| Free-tier rate limit hit during peak use | Medium | Medium | Show friendly "slow down" message with countdown |
| Incomplete historical data (pre-1980s) | High | Low | Add in-app note that data coverage varies by era |
| API schema change breaking the app | Low | High | Pin to `/nba/v1`; monitor API changelog |

